{"title":"民族精神赞","authors":["时延春"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族精神赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时延春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场鏖战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却看不见硝烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场搏斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却听不到呐喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场特殊战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却没有炮舰导弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是病魔的突然袭击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是对民族精神的挑战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不屈的中华民族魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历了五千年考验。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的航船乘风破浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕过了多少惊涛险滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的脊梁永远挺直，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承受了多少浩劫灾难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的伟岸之躯越发强壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶住了多少狂风雷电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打一场人民战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗号令传遍塞北江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群防群控，各自为战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一方有难，八方支援。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱响时代的最强音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱写时代的新诗篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族凝聚力筑起钢铁长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族精神光耀万年。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}